********************************************************************************
3rd party graphics
********************************************************************************
Title screen logo font is based off Audiowide
 Copyright (c) 2012, Brian J. Bonislawsky DBA Astigmatic (AOETI)
 Licensed under the SIL Open Font License, Version 1.1

Dialog & menu font is based off Deathwake font by Zee-3
 http://www.zee-3.com/pickfordbros/archive/bitmapfonts.php
 "Feel free to use any of these fonts for whatever purpose you see fit."

Some text is based off the Tragic Marker font 
 Copyright (c) 2016 Missy Meyer
 http://missymeyer.com/tragic-marker
 "Free for personal and commercial use"

Some scenery is based off tilesets created by Sithjester
 http://untamed.wild-refuge.net/rpgxp.php
 "Feel free to use my resources as you want, be it in free or commercial games,
 edited how you want, as bases for your own sprites, or for non-RPG Maker stuff"

********************************************************************************
3rd party music
********************************************************************************
bgm_title.esf is a conversion of Chip Overture by Drozerix
 Released under the Public Domain license
 https://creativecommons.org/licenses/publicdomain/
 "Feel free to use my music in whatever, pc game, video, program, keygen ext."
 Original XM: /src/music/Drozerix_chip_overture.xm

bgm_end.esf is a conversion of The Radix Point by Drozerix
 Released under the Public Domain license
 https://creativecommons.org/licenses/publicdomain/
 "Feel free to use my music in whatever, pc game, video, program, keygen ext."
 Original song was modified so all percussion was on a single track so it 
 could be mapped to the PCM channel - modifications are also Public Domain
 Original XM is - /src/music/Drozerix_chip_overture.xm
 No modifications were made
 Original XM: /src/music/Drozerix_the_radix_point.xm
 Modified XM: /src/music/Drozerix_the_radix_point_mod.xm

bgm_day00.esf is a conversion of October Chip by Drozerix
 Released under the Public Domain license
 https://creativecommons.org/licenses/publicdomain/
 "Feel free to use my music in whatever, pc game, video, program, keygen ext."
 Original song was modified to remove percussion from track 6 and 
 the intro was cut so it only plays the looping section
 Original XM: /src/music/Drozerix_october_chip.xm
 Modified XM: /src/music/Drozerix_october_chip_mainloop.xm

bgm_store00.esf is a conversion of The Spirit of Mods by Blurry
 Licensed under the Attribution Share Alike license
 https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/
 Original song was modified to:
  -Reduce the number of instruments used in some tracks
  -Remove fade out and loop timing
 Changes are under the same license as the original work
 Original XM: /src/music/blurry_the_spirit_of_mods.xm
 Modified XM: /src/music/blurry_the_spirit_of_mods_mod.xm

